        <h2>
            Issues that Homosexuals, Bisexuals and Transgenders Face:
        </h2>
        <ul>
            They face violence at disproportionately high retes compared to straight people.
        </ul>
        <ul>
            They have been treated unfairly because of their gender identity.
        </ul>
        <ul>
            Some of them have faced poverty due to anti-LGBT discrimination.
        </ul>
        <ul>
            They are more likely than straight people to report unmet health needs.
        </ul>
        <ul>
            Some pinoys want gay folks to live by their established stereotypes.
        </ul>
        
